XtTranslateCoords(3)                                                                           XT FUNCTIONS                                                                           XtTranslateCoords(3)

NAME
       XtTranslateCoords - translate widget coordinates

SYNTAX
       #include <X11/Intrinsic.h>

       void XtTranslateCoords(Widget w, Position x, Position y, Position *rootx_return, Position *rooty_return);

ARGUMENTS
       rootx_return
       rooty_return
                 Returns the root-relative x and y coordinates.

       x
       y         Specify the widget-relative x and y coordinates.

       w         Specifies the widget.

DESCRIPTION
       While XtTranslateCoords is similar to the Xlib XTranslateCoordinates function, it does not generate a server request because all the required information already is in the widget's data struc‚Äê
       tures.

